{"tid":826530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可口可樂被爆擬推「健康」大麻飲料","createTime":"2018-09-18T09:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T03:28:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":244,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"066f3e93532b57f2e0ff25a1c6be938840c534e9","tid":826530,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180918/640_c592ac07dbb30bed7a5d15a3d175a576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180918%2F640_c592ac07dbb30bed7a5d15a3d175a576.jpg&h=abc58c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據加拿大《BNN彭博》（BNN Bloomberg）周一報導，可口可樂公司計畫開發「健康」導向的大麻飲料，目前正與加國大麻生產商「極光大麻」（Aurora Cannabis）進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士稱，兩家公司可能合作開發出具有消炎、止痛、舒緩肌肉痙攣的健康飲料。《BNN彭博》報導，無法確定雙方談判會否成功，即便成功也不一定會公開協議內容。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂在聲明中表示，公司和許多飲品業者一樣，都在關注添加大麻二酚（CBD）於功能性健康飲料的可能性，目前尚未做出任何定論，亦不回應任何猜測。極光大麻公司則稱，確實打算進入飲料市場。<br />\n<br />\n大麻二酚為大麻主要成分之一，有助抗焦慮、抗氧化、抗炎等作用，現有研究中未發現顯著副作用，被認為成癮性較低。在美國娛樂用大麻合法化的地區，不少廠商強調其產品只含有大麻二酚成份。而加拿大已準備在下月將娛樂用大麻完全合法。<br />\n<br />\n北美啤酒商巨頭摩紳庫爾斯釀酒公司（Molson Coors Brewing），以及知名啤酒品牌可樂娜的製造商星座集團（Constellation Brands），日前都已宣布將投資大麻飲料研發。可口可樂傳出跟進消息後，股價在美股開盤前微幅上漲。（林宜萱／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/ny/realtime/20180918/1431803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fny%2Frealtime%2F20180918%2F1431803&d=KStb7oAJy0v30uX54xUqctU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d025a412\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fny%2Frealtime%2F20180918%2F1431803&h=518728a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/ny/realtime/20180918/1431803</a>"},{"pid":"6b146d049e55ce9d63388f3a95d88247a30305e9","tid":826530,"uid":6030,"like":175,"dislike":3,"score":172,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"香港實冇啦"},{"pid":"41e1297881bb3c45542c0f26aecdf4e861ad268d","tid":826530,"uid":53026,"like":149,"dislike":1,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"火麻仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5bc4325c60783b4ffe75386dcc5b36e92de5f8","tid":826530,"uid":14715,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"香港CBD 好似合法."},{"pid":"d8473f87c65ec669c8e6cc8c1636ff1112fe457e","tid":826530,"uid":89514,"like":43,"dislike":8,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50af52b8943afaefc393dc266fa96dcb3e83e633","tid":826530,"uid":60655,"like":394,"dislike":1,"score":393,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/183154_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F183154_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3dc4627a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5d91245732aa280ad2641098b5e4c2f63761335","tid":826530,"uid":208722,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"d8473f87c65ec669c8e6cc8c1636ff1112fe457e","tid":826530,"uid":89514,"like":43,"dislike":8,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"係雞係公廁"},{"pid":"9668e0a7d85c597bc4d2e705e8db7d4241e58a9e","tid":826530,"uid":14715,"like":81,"dislike":46,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"d8473f87c65ec669c8e6cc8c1636ff1112fe457e","tid":826530,"uid":89514,"like":43,"dislike":8,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"香港人見到大麻已經嚇到灑手擰頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會去了解下係咩來。"},{"pid":"58694a233dc84c9732de22cdae3aee8f700d928b","tid":826530,"uid":89514,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a9369ff40ac7262432c9d4cbbaa2f6717a92c04","tid":826530,"uid":102872,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"想飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d7fccbc5e5477c6707a65a1f0ec206a6575277","tid":826530,"uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":32,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"9668e0a7d85c597bc4d2e705e8db7d4241e58a9e","tid":826530,"uid":14715,"like":81,"dislike":46,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"d8473f87c65ec669c8e6cc8c1636ff1112fe457e","tid":826530,"uid":89514,"like":43,"dislike":8,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"香港人見到大麻已經嚇到灑手擰頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會去了解下係咩來。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"所以呢班港豬生CANCER以為無得醫係抵死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d545c14ed0c4e36ed30cda4ffde3525c9d5f42c2","tid":826530,"uid":29880,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:36:55.000Z","msg":"drink weed everyday<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3c653eb81a97a6c51afa46c2be007c9f6d4a30","tid":826530,"uid":80814,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"可口可樂出嘅，我有興趣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a694fb92361bade7b7cf73d3de4e3929578747","tid":826530,"uid":14715,"like":105,"dislike":3,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"那麼CBD是不是&quot;大麻&quot;呢？若果根據以上定義的話，可見香港的法例是把Marijuana與Hemp分開的，因為它指明是&rdquo;含有四氫大麻酚的任何大麻屬植物&rdquo;，這就是指Marijuana這種THC含量高於0.3%的大麻，<br />\n<br />\n而若果他們把Hemp包含在內的話，所有的麻繩、麻布、麻紙或纖維等都是非法，因為它們就是大麻屬植物的任何部份，可見香港的法例是針對THC，這種大麻中的精神活性物質；<br />\n<br />\n加上火麻仁是有CBD，若他們是禁CBD的話，火麻仁應該一早是非法涼茶。<br />\n加上現在的科技，CBD已經能獨立的分離出來，由此可以推斷純CBD並不是法例所指的&rdquo;大麻&quot;。"},{"pid":"baaf246665528725fca851bfeaa4afbe6ebb3084","tid":826530,"uid":65400,"like":50,"dislike":26,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"道友全面進場"},{"pid":"9d9d7de3619cdd8b1e5de2f3854d928a41a392b1","tid":826530,"uid":178205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"決定入多啲zero贊助佢整<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c830d230c608966c045205290239d1209866d54b","tid":826530,"uid":36658,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T10:49:11.000Z","msg":"抽返枝健康大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea099f26388ef2c16694eda8fd8aa165742402f","tid":826530,"uid":57214,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"真鬼佬涼茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92eb0b4d8813d4535fb13371e773e816e6fe7d0","tid":826530,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"香港邊到有真材實料既火麻仁?"},{"pid":"8d7d7b82cd436070a25b365c58f0d6e7156e19a8","tid":826530,"uid":16846,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"飲健康茶 吸健康大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78713e70e090d35ff2f89218653e94ce5dd5cdf1","tid":826530,"uid":50740,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"連登道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fd9174d97ef64f7c64ab39a1e68b4da7071407","tid":826530,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"今次真係加了大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg